:FED.
5.4 Reporting claims
:SKRSLUT.
.br
SOS International must be informed without delay in the event of injury.
On returning home, a claim report is to be submitted to Privatsikring
together with documentation for extra expenses, a statement from the
physician who treated the insured during the journey, as well as any other
information relevant to the treatment of the injury.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
